Fanatix,is,a,gamified,social,sports,watching,app,The,app,includes,both,basic,game,viewing,and,social,check,in,functions,Users,can,access,basic,game,information,and,sign,up,for,score,alerts,as,well,as,seeing,which,friends,of,theirs,are,also,watching,the,same,game,Check,ins,win,users,points,that,are,rewarded,with,prizes,such,as,game,tickets,and,electronics,The,Fanatix,API,is,only,available,by,request,and,is,intended,for,the,development,of,other,apps